overflow:auto'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Courier New";
color:black'>sudo nano /usr/share/nginx/www/info.php</span></pre>

<p class=MsoNormal style='background:white'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
14.5pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";color:black'>Add in the following line:</span></p>

<pre style='margin-top:21.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:21.0pt;margin-left:
